WEBVTT

00:02.102 --> 00:03.469
All right.
Here's the bet.

00:03.937 --> 00:05.806
For 10 bucks

00:05.839 --> 00:07.473
I drink this much
of anything.

00:08.642 --> 00:09.676
Anything?

00:10.711 --> 00:11.878
Anything.

00:11.912 --> 00:13.947
As long as
it's something
you can eat.

00:13.980 --> 00:15.315
Okay, only stuff
from the kitchen.

00:15.348 --> 00:17.250
Nothing from the bathroom
and nothing from the garage.

00:17.283 --> 00:18.251
Okay.

00:18.284 --> 00:20.420
And it has to be food, okay?

00:20.453 --> 00:22.022
Nothing from under
the sink.

00:22.055 --> 00:24.224
Okay? No cleansers,
no detergent.

00:24.257 --> 00:28.494
No furniture polish
and no cut up bits of sponge.

00:29.495 --> 00:30.764
Okay.

00:30.797 --> 00:33.233
I'm just trying
to win 10 bucks here.
I don't wanna die.

00:33.867 --> 00:36.169
All right, now put on...

00:36.937 --> 00:38.572
The blindfold.

00:40.006 --> 00:41.508
I don't want to
mess up my hair.

00:43.243 --> 00:45.478
All right.
And now step into

00:45.512 --> 00:47.280
the sound proof booth.

00:50.951 --> 00:52.519
I'm trusting you guys.

00:56.489 --> 00:58.491
Okay, put in some mustard.
It's an ipecac.

00:58.525 --> 00:59.593
It'll make him barf.

00:59.626 --> 01:03.229
Don't make him barf.
My mom cooks dinner in here!

01:03.263 --> 01:04.765
If we're not trying
to make him barf,

01:04.798 --> 01:06.567
then why are we
doing this?

01:06.600 --> 01:09.503
I can hear everything
you guys are saying.

01:09.536 --> 01:12.005
Come on, Bill!
Quit listening!

01:12.038 --> 01:13.239
I can't help it.

01:13.273 --> 01:15.408
Then hum so
you can't hear us.

01:16.743 --> 01:19.212
(HUMMING)

01:19.245 --> 01:20.514
Cayenne pepper.

01:20.547 --> 01:22.215
Ooh! Good one!

01:22.248 --> 01:23.950
Pass me
the pickle juice.

01:23.984 --> 01:25.819
(HUMMING)

01:25.852 --> 01:27.854
You know, my cousin

01:27.888 --> 01:30.190
once drank an entire jar
of pickle juice.

01:30.223 --> 01:32.726
He had to sit
on the toilet
for 10 hours.

01:32.759 --> 01:35.128
SAM: Oh, God,
that's nasty!

01:35.161 --> 01:37.130
NEAL: Oh, this is
gonna be great.

01:37.564 --> 01:38.565
Salt...

01:39.566 --> 01:41.101
