01:41.134 --> 01:42.836
SAM: Aw!
Disgusting!

01:42.869 --> 01:44.871
SAM: Oh, man!
(HUMMING)

01:44.905 --> 01:46.873
Vinegar! Mmm...

01:46.907 --> 01:48.642
Wait, wait...
Vinegar!

01:48.675 --> 01:49.743
Soy sauce.

01:50.476 --> 01:51.612
Soy sauce!

01:51.645 --> 01:53.446
