01:53.479 --> 01:54.748
Chili!

01:54.781 --> 01:56.382
For texture.

01:56.416 --> 01:59.419
NEAL: That's disgusting!
Exactly!

01:59.452 --> 02:02.355
NEAL: And just
a little bit of jelly.

02:02.388 --> 02:04.190
SAM: Some dairy creamer.

02:04.558 --> 02:05.592
And...

02:05.626 --> 02:07.493
Top it all off,

02:07.528 --> 02:09.763
a couple of
after‐dinner mints.

02:09.796 --> 02:11.097
(LAUGHS)

02:11.131 --> 02:12.465
All right.

02:13.900 --> 02:15.769
SAM: Now mix it up.
All right.

02:19.840 --> 02:22.776
